{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775885397756,"sessionID":"ses_284fdf7d7ffeSBtDzQQva0Cy9z","part":{"id":"prt_d7b03d28c001CPx1joB0nfd370","messageID":"msg_d7b03bf82001X51sizThLPIFCm","sessionID":"ses_284fdf7d7ffeSBtDzQQva0Cy9z","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_f1c5bf4a91e14fc99ca641e4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/AR-035-verification-report.md","content":"# AR-035 Verification Report: client-go Type Client Generation\n\n## Summary\n\n**Status**: ❌ **PARTIAL IMPLEMENTATION - BUILD FAILURES**\n\nThe client-go library implementation matches the spec for the core typed client interfaces, but has **critical build errors** that prevent compilation. Several required files are missing or have incorrect code.\n\n---\n\n## API Contract Verification\n\n### ✅ Clientset (`clientset/versioned/clientset.go`)\n\n**Status**: ✅ **COMPLIANT**\n\n| Requirement | Spec | Implementation | Status |\n|-------------|------|----------------|--------|\n| `Interface` definition | `Discovery()`, `RuntimeV1alpha1()` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `Clientset` struct | Embeds `*discovery.DiscoveryClient`, `runtimeV1alpha1` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config)` | Returns `(*Clientset, error)` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client)` | Returns `(*Clientset, error)` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config)` | Returns `*Clientset` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `New(c rest.Interface)` | Returns `*Clientset` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1()` accessor | Returns `runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Typed Client - `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` (`runtime_client.go`)\n\n**Status**: ✅ **COMPLIANT**\n\n| Requirement | Spec | Implementation | Status |\n|-------------|------|----------------|--------|\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` | `RESTClient()`, `AgentRuntimesGetter`, `CodeInterpretersGetter` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` struct | Holds `restClient rest.Interface` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `NewForConfig()` | Configures GroupVersion, APIPath, NegotiatedSerializer | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `NewForConfigAndClient()` | Same config + http.Client | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `New()` | Takes `rest.Interface` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| REST defaults | GroupVersion = `SchemeGroupVersion`, APIPath = `/apis` | ✅ Correct | ✅ |\n| `AgentRuntimes(namespace)` | Returns `AgentRuntimeInterface` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `CodeInterpreters(namespace)` | Returns `CodeInterpreterInterface` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ AgentRuntimeInterface (`agentruntime.go`)\n\n**Status**: ✅ **COMPLIANT**\n\n| Method | Spec Signature | Implementation | Status |\n|--------|---------------|----------------|--------|\n| `Create` | `(ctx, *AgentRuntime, CreateOptions) (*AgentRuntime, error)` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `Update` | `(ctx, *AgentRuntime, UpdateOptions) (*AgentRuntime, error)` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `UpdateStatus` | `(ctx, *AgentRuntime, UpdateOptions) (*AgentRuntime, error)` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `Delete` | `(ctx, name string, DeleteOptions) error` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `DeleteCollection` | `(ctx, DeleteOptions, ListOptions) error` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `Get` | `(ctx, name string, GetOptions) (*AgentRuntime, error)` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `List` | `(ctx, ListOptions) (*AgentRuntimeList, error)` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `Watch` | `(ctx, ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `Patch` | `(ctx, name, PatchType, data, opts, ...subresources) (*AgentRuntime, error)` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| Embeds | `AgentRuntimeExpansion` | ✅ Present | ✅ |\n| Resource plural | `agentruntimes` | ✅ Correct | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ CodeInterpreterInterface (`codeinterpreter.go`)\n\n**Status**: ✅ **COMPLIANT**\n\n| Requirement | Spec | Implementation | Status |\n|-------------|------|----------------|--------|\n| Method shape | Same as `AgentRuntimeInterface` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| Types | `*CodeInterpreter` / `CodeInterpreterList` | ✅ Correct | ✅ |\n| Resource plural | `codeinterpreters` | ✅ Correct | ✅ |\n| Expansion | `CodeInterpreterExpansion` | ✅ Present | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Expansion Hooks (`generated_expansion.go`)\n\n**Status**: ✅ **COMPLIANT**\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeExpansion interface{}\ntype CodeInterpreterExpansion interface{}\n```\nEmpty interfaces reserved for custom methods - as specified.\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Getter Interfaces (`generated_getters.go`)\n\n**Status**: ✅ **COMPLIANT**\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimesGetter interface {\n    AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeInterface\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpretersGetter interface {\n    CodeInterpreters(namespace string) CodeInterpreterInterface\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ Scheme (`clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`)\n\n**Status**: ❌ **BUILD ERROR**\n\n**Issues Found:**\n\n1. **`serializer.NewCodecGroup` undefined** (line 31)\n   - Current: `var Codecs = serializer.NewCodecGroup(Scheme)`\n   - The `NewCodecGroup` function doesn't exist in `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/serializer`\n   \n2. **`runtime.SchemeBuilder` type misuse** (line 36)\n   - Current: `var localSchemeBuilder = &runtime.SchemeBuilder`\n   - `SchemeBuilder` is a type, not a variable. Should use `runtime.NewSchemeBuilder()`\n\n**Expected fix:**\n```go\nvar Codecs = serializer.NewCodec(Scheme)  // or direct serializer setup\nvar localSchemeBuilder = runtime.NewSchemeBuilder(runtimev1alpha1.AddToScheme)\n```\n\n---\n\n### ❌ Listers (`listers/runtime/v1alpha1/`)\n\n**Status**: ❌ **BUILD ERROR - MISSING IMPORTS**\n\n**File**: `agentruntime.go`\n\n**Issues:**\n1. Missing import: `labels` package (used in `labels.Selector`)\n2. Missing import: `runtimev1alpha1` package (used for `*AgentRuntime` types)\n3. Missing import: `errors` package (used in `errors.NewNotFound`)\n4. Missing import: `runtimev1alpha1.Resource()` function\n\n**Current imports (line 21-23):**\n```go\nimport (\n    cache \"k8s.io/client-go/tools/cache\"\n)\n```\n\n**Required imports:**\n```go\nimport (\n    errors \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors\"\n    labels \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/labels\"\n    runtimev1alpha1 \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n    cache \"k8s.io/client-go/tools/cache\"\n)\n```\n\n**Same issues in**: `codeinterpreter.go`\n\n---\n\n### ❌ Informer Factory (`informers/externalversions/factory.go`)\n\n**Status**: ❌ **BUILD ERROR - MISSING IMPORTS + INCOMPLETE STRUCT**\n\n**Issues:**\n\n1. **Missing imports:**\n   - `time` package (used for `time.Duration`)\n   - `fmt` package (used for `fmt.Errorf`)\n   - `runtimev1alpha1` package (used for `SchemeGroupVersion`)\n\n2. **Struct definition exposed** (lines 34-44):\n   - `sharedInformerFactory` struct is defined in factory.go but should be in internalinterfaces or not exposed\n   - The struct references conflict with internalinterfaces package\n\n3. **Missing runtime informer interface package**:\n   - Error: `no required module provides package github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime`\n   - The `runtime/interface.go` file is **MISSING**\n\n---\n\n### ❌ Missing Required Files\n\nPer the spec, the following files are **MISSING**:\n\n| Path | Role | Status |\n|------|------|--------|\n| `informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go` | Group runtime informer accessor | ❌ MISSING |\n| `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go` | v1alpha1 informer accessors | ❌ MISSING |\n| `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | AgentRuntime informer + constructor | ❌ MISSING |\n| `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | CodeInterpreter informer + constructor | ❌ MISSING |\n| `informers/externalversions/generic.go` | GenericInformer, ForResource | ❌ MISSING |\n| `client-go/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` | (may exist elsewhere) | ? |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Fake Clients (`typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/`)\n\n**Status**: ✅ **FILES PRESENT** (not fully verified)\n\nFiles exist:\n- `fake_runtime_client.go`\n- `fake_agentruntime.go`\n- `fake_codeinterpreter.go`\n- `doc.go`\n\n*(Detailed API contract verification pending - requires reading fake implementation files)*\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Clientset Versioned Fake (`clientset/versioned/fake/`)\n\n**Status**: ✅ **FILES PRESENT**\n\nFiles exist:\n- `clientset_generated.go`\n- `register.go`\n- `doc.go`\n\n---\n\n## Build Test Results\n\n```bash\n$ go test ./client-go/...\n# github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/informers/externalversions\nclient-go/informers/externalversions/factory.go:27:2: no required module provides package github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime\n\n# github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme\nclient-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go:31:25: undefined: serializer.NewCodecGroup\nclient-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go:36:27: runtime.SchemeBuilder (type) is not an expression\n\n# github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1\nclient-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go:27:16: undefined: labels\nclient-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go:27:37: undefined: runtimev1alpha1\n# ... (many more undefined errors)\n```\n\n**Result**: ❌ **BUILD FAILED** - 0 tests executed\n\n---\n\n## Compliance Summary\n\n| Component | Files Present | API Compliant | Builds | Status |\n|-----------|--------------|---------------|--------|--------|\n| Clientset | ✅ | ✅ | ⚠️ (depends on scheme) | ⚠️ |\n| Typed Client (runtime/v1alpha1) | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ (scheme error) | ❌ |\n| AgentRuntime interface | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ (depends on scheme) | ❌ |\n| CodeInterpreter interface | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ (depends on scheme) | ❌ |\n| Scheme | ✅ | ⚠️ | ❌ | ❌ |\n| Listers | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ (missing imports) | ❌ |\n| Informers | ⚠️ (incomplete) | N/A | ❌ (missing files) | ❌ |\n| Fake clients | ✅ | Not verified | ❌ (depends) | ⚠️ |\n| Expansion hooks | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n## Critical Issues Blocking Deployment\n\n1. **Scheme registration broken** - `serializer.NewCodecGroup` doesn't exist\n2. **Listers missing imports** - Cannot compile without `labels`, `runtimev1alpha1`, `errors`\n3. **Informer infrastructure incomplete** - Missing 5+ critical files\n4. **Factory struct conflict** - `sharedInformerFactory` definition issues\n\n---\n\n## Recommendations\n\n### P0 - Fix Build Errors\n\n1. **Fix `scheme/register.go`**:\n   - Replace `serializer.NewCodecGroup(Scheme)` with proper serializer setup\n   - Fix `SchemeBuilder` usage to use `runtime.NewSchemeBuilder()`\n\n2. **Fix listers imports**:\n   - Add missing imports to `agentruntime.go` and `codeinterpreter.go`\n\n3. **Generate missing informer files**:\n   - Run `make gen-client` or `hack/update-codegen.sh` to generate:\n     - `informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go`\n     - `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go`\n     - `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n     - `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n     - `informers/externalversions/generic.go`\n\n4. **Fix factory.go**:\n   - Add missing imports (`time`, `fmt`, `runtimev1alpha1`)\n   - Resolve struct definition conflict\n\n### P1 - Complete Verification\n\n5. Verify fake client implementations match interface contracts\n6. Add integration tests for client-go\n7. Verify code generation script works end-to-end\n\n---\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThe **API contracts and interface definitions are correctly implemented** according to the spec. However, the implementation has **critical build errors** that prevent compilation:\n\n- Core typed clients: ✅ Spec compliant\n- Scheme registration: ❌ Broken\n- Listers: ❌ Missing imports\n- Informers: ❌ Incomplete (missing files)\n\n**Cannot pass quality gate until build errors are resolved.**\n\n---\n\n**Verification Date**: 2026-04-11\n**Verifier**: opencode\n**Spec Version**: deployment/client-go.md\n**Next Steps**: Fix P0 