==========================================\n--- /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/AR-035-verification-report.md\n+++ /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/AR-035-verification-report.md\n@@ -374,20 +374,34 @@\n 1. **Fix `scheme/register.go`**:\n    - Replace `serializer.NewCodecGroup(Scheme)` with proper serializer setup\n    - Fix `SchemeBuilder` usage to use `runtime.NewSchemeBuilder()`\n \n-2. **Fix listers imports**:\n-   - Add missing imports to `agentruntime.go` and `codeinterpreter.go`\n+2. **Fix typed client imports** (`agentruntime.go`, `codeinterpreter.go`):\n+   - Add missing import: `scheme \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme\"`\n \n-3. **Generate missing informer files**:\n+3. **Fix listers imports** (`agentruntime.go`, `codeinterpreter.go` in listers/):\n+   - Add missing imports: `labels`, `runtimev1alpha1`, `errors`\n+\n+4. **Fix fake client implementation**:\n+   - Ensure `FakeRuntimeV1alpha1` properly embeds `*testing.Fake`\n+   - Fix `Invokes` and `InvokesWatch` method calls\n+   - Fix `NewListAction` to use 4-argument signature with GVK\n+   - Fix `FakeClientset` to properly implement interfaces\n+\n+5. **Investigate pkg/apis types**:\n+   - Verify `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` types embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n+   - Verify `DeepCopyObject()` method is generated correctly in `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n+   - Check if types satisfy `runtime.Object` interface\n+\n+6. **Generate missing informer files**:\n    - Run `make gen-client` or `hack/update-codegen.sh` to generate:\n      - `informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go`\n      - `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go`\n      - `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n      - `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n      - `informers/externalversions/generic.go`\n \n-4. **Fix factory.go**:\n+7. **Fix factory.go**:\n    - Add missing imports (`time`, `fmt`, `runtimev1alpha1`)\n    - Resolve struct definition conflict\n \n ### P1 - Complete Verification\n","filediff":{"file":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/AR-035-verification-report.md","before":"# AR-035 Verification Report: client-go Type Client Generation\n\n## Summary\n\n**Status**: ❌ **PARTIAL IMPLEMENTATION - BUILD FAILURES**\n\nThe client-go library implementation matches the spec for the core typed client interfaces, but has **critical build errors** that prevent compilation. Several required files are missing or have incorrect code.\n\n### Additional Critical Issues Found (LSP Diagnostics)\n\nAfter initial verification, LSP diagnostics revealed **additional severe issues**:\n\n1. **Missing `scheme` import** in `agentruntime.go` and `codeinterpreter.go` - uses undefined `scheme.ParameterCodec`\n2. **Missing `DeepCopyObject` method** on AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter types - generated deepcopy code exists but types don't implement runtime.Object interface\n3. **Fake client broken** - `FakeRuntimeV1alpha1` missing `Invokes` and `InvokesWatch` methods, wrong `NewListAction` signature\n4. **Fake clientset broken** - `FakeClientset` doesn't properly embed `testing.Fake`\n\n---\n\n## API Contract Verification\n\n### ✅ Clientset (`clientset/versioned/clientset.go`)\n\n**Status**: ✅ **COMPLIANT**\n\n| Requirement | Spec | Implementation | Status |\n|-------------|------|----------------|--------|\n| `Interface` definition | `Discovery()`, `RuntimeV1alpha1()` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `Clientset` struct | Embeds `*discovery.DiscoveryClient`, `runtimeV1alpha1` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config)` | Returns `(*Clientset, error)` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client)` | Returns `(*Clientset, error)` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config)` | Returns `*Clientset` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `New(c rest.Interface)` | Returns `*Clientset` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1()` accessor | Returns `runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Typed Client - `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` (`runtime_client.go`)\n\n**Status**: ✅ **COMPLIANT**\n\n| Requirement | Spec | Implementation | Status |\n|-------------|------|----------------|--------|\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` | `RESTClient()`, `AgentRuntimesGetter`, `CodeInterpretersGetter` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` struct | Holds `restClient rest.Interface` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `NewForConfig()` | Configures GroupVersion, APIPath, NegotiatedSerializer | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `NewForConfigAndClient()` | Same config + http.Client | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `New()` | Takes `rest.Interface` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| REST defaults | GroupVersion = `SchemeGroupVersion`, APIPath = `/apis` | ✅ Correct | ✅ |\n| `AgentRuntimes(namespace)` | Returns `AgentRuntimeInterface` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n| `CodeInterpreters(namespace)` | Returns `CodeInterpreterInterface` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ AgentRuntimeInterface (`agentruntime.go`)\n\n**Status**: ✅ **COMPLIANT**\n\n| Method | Spec Signature | Implementation | Status |\n|--------|---------------|----------------|--------|\n| `Create` | `(ctx, *AgentRuntime, CreateOptions) (*AgentRuntime, error)` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `Update` | `(ctx, *AgentRuntime, UpdateOptions) (*AgentRuntime, error)` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `UpdateStatus` | `(ctx, *AgentRuntime, UpdateOptions) (*AgentRuntime, error)` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `Delete` | `(ctx, name string, DeleteOptions) error` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `DeleteCollection` | `(ctx, DeleteOptions, ListOptions) error` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `Get` | `(ctx, name string, GetOptions) (*AgentRuntime, error)` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `List` | `(ctx, ListOptions) (*AgentRuntimeList, error)` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `Watch` | `(ctx, ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| `Patch` | `(ctx, name, PatchType, data, opts, ...subresources) (*AgentRuntime, error)` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| Embeds | `AgentRuntimeExpansion` | ✅ Present | ✅ |\n| Resource plural | `agentruntimes` | ✅ Correct | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ CodeInterpreterInterface (`codeinterpreter.go`)\n\n**Status**: ✅ **COMPLIANT**\n\n| Requirement | Spec | Implementation | Status |\n|-------------|------|----------------|--------|\n| Method shape | Same as `AgentRuntimeInterface` | ✅ Matches | ✅ |\n| Types | `*CodeInterpreter` / `CodeInterpreterList` | ✅ Correct | ✅ |\n| Resource plural | `codeinterpreters` | ✅ Correct | ✅ |\n| Expansion | `CodeInterpreterExpansion` | ✅ Present | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Expansion Hooks (`generated_expansion.go`)\n\n**Status**: ✅ **COMPLIANT**\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeExpansion interface{}\ntype CodeInterpreterExpansion interface{}\n```\nEmpty interfaces reserved for custom methods - as specified.\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Getter Interfaces (`generated_getters.go`)\n\n**Status**: ✅ **COMPLIANT**\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimesGetter interface {\n    AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeInterface\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpretersGetter interface {\n    CodeInterpreters(namespace string) CodeInterpreterInterface\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ Scheme (`clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`)\n\n**Status**: ❌ **BUILD ERROR**\n\n**Issues Found:**\n\n1. **`serializer.NewCodecGroup` undefined** (line 31)\n   - Current: `var Codecs = serializer.NewCodecGroup(Scheme)`\n   - The `NewCodecGroup` function doesn't exist in `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/serializer`\n   \n2. **`runtime.SchemeBuilder` type misuse** (line 36)\n   - Current: `var localSchemeBuilder = &runtime.SchemeBuilder`\n   - `SchemeBuilder` is a type, not a variable. Should use `runtime.NewSchemeBuilder()`\n\n**Expected fix:**\n```go\nvar Codecs = serializer.NewCodec(Scheme)  // or direct serializer setup\nvar localSchemeBuilder = runtime.NewSchemeBuilder(